          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ". N,GAMMA capture cross section of Pa-233 in neutron",
                " energy from 0 to 1 MeV was deduced via the product",
                " of measured gamma emission probability Pgam of",
                " excited Pa-234 which was measured between 5.2 and 6.2",
                " MeV excitation energy using transfer reaction",
                " Th-232(He-3,p)Pa-234exc, see table under this keyword,",
                " Table 2 of main reference.",
                " It is assumed that population of states in Pa-234exc",
                " is the same for both Th-232(He-3,p) and Pa-233(n,g)",
                " reactions. MCNP 4C2 transport code was used for this",
                " process simulations.",
                "*    E-exc,MeV         Pgam, Nodim Pgam-err",
                "*      4.92             1.03         0.07",
                "*      5.12             1.02         0.07",
                "*      5.32             0.65         0.05",
                "*      5.52             0.49         0.04",
                "*      5.72             0.43         0.03",
                "*      5.92             0.39         0.03",
                "*      6.12             0.51         0.03"
              ]
            }
          ],
